collectionMetadata.name: CPF Contribution Rates, Allocation Rates and Applicable Wage Ceiling
collectionMetadata.description: Rates of CPF contribution for employers or employees, allocation rates for various age groups & account types, and applicable wage ceiling

datasetMetadata.name: CPF contribution rates
datasetMetadata.description:
As a proportion of wage, for private sector employees and public sector non-pensionable employees.
Percentages are expressed as a number out of 1.
The CPF contribution rates are applicable for the highest wage band. For example, the rates for January 2014 are applicable for wages of $750 or more per month.

datasetMetadata.name: CPF allocation rates
datasetMetadata.description:
As a proportion of wage, for private sector employees, public sector non-pensionable employees.
Percentages are expressed as a number out of 1.
The rates are applicable for the highest wage band. For example, the rates for January 2014 are applicable for wages of $750 or more per month.
